== 反應 ==
氢氧化钡在 800 °C以上分解成[[氧化钡|氧化钡]]。它和[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]反应，形成[[碳酸钡|碳酸钡]]。氢氧化钡水溶液是强碱性的，会和酸中和。因此，它分别和硫酸和磷酸反应，形成[[硫酸钡|硫酸钡]]和[[磷酸钡|磷酸钡]]。氢氧化钡和[[硫化氢|硫化氢]]反应，形成[[硫化钡|硫化钡]]。当氢氧化钡水溶液与其它金属盐溶液混合时，会产生不溶性或难溶性钡盐的沉淀，可能是由置换反应引起的。<ref>Pradyot Patnaik. ''Handbook of Inorganic Chemicals''. McGraw-Hill, 2002, {{ISBN|0-07-049439-8}}</ref>

氢氧化钡和[[铵盐|铵盐]]的反应是强{{le|吸热过程|endothermic}}。八水合氢氧化钡和[[氯化铵|氯化铵]]<ref name=UCSD>{{cite web|title=Endothermic Reactions of Hydrated Barium Hydroxide and Ammonium Chloride|url=http://www-chem.ucsd.edu/undergraduate/teaching-labs/demos/demo45.html|publisher=UC San Diego|access-date=2 April 2014|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115210341/https://www-chem.ucsd.edu/undergraduate/teaching-labs/demos/demo45.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nuffieldfoundation.org/practical-chemistry/endothermic-solid-solid-reactions |title=Endothermic Solid-Solid Reactions |access-date=2021-07-14 |archive-date=2016-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160714025734/http://www.nuffieldfoundation.org/practical-chemistry/endothermic-solid-solid-reactions |dead-url=no }}</ref> 或[[硫氰酸铵|硫氰酸铵]]<ref name=UW>{{cite web|last=Camp|first=Eric|title=Endothermic Reaction|url=http://depts.washington.edu/chem/facilserv/lecturedemo/EndothermicReaction-UWDept.ofChemistry.html|publisher=Univertist of Washington|access-date=2 April 2014|archive-date=2020-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200110205514/http://depts.washington.edu/chem/facilserv/lecturedemo/EndothermicReaction-UWDept.ofChemistry.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=RSC>{{cite web|title=Endothermic solid-solid reactions |url=http://media.rsc.org/Classic%20Chem%20Demos/CCD-44.pdf |work=Classic Chemistry Demonstrations |publisher=The Royal Society of Chemistry |access-date=2 April 2014 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407092124/http://media.rsc.org/Classic%20Chem%20Demos/CCD-44.pdf |archive-date=7 April 2014 }}</ref> 的反应通常用作课堂化学演示，会产生足够冷的温度以冻结水。

== 危险性 ==
类似于其他的[[强碱|强碱]]，氢氧化钡具有[[腐蚀性|腐蚀性]]。

